<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>404 — ShortLink</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #000;
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(5rem, 18vw, 10rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
      color: #fff;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    p.sub {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #888;
      max-width: 420px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .cards {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .card {
      border: 1px solid #222;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      width: 200px;
      text-align: left;
      background: transparent;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .card:hover { border-color: #555; }

    .card .label {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #666;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .btn:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #fff;
      color: #000;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      border: 1px solid #333;
      color: #aaa;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="badge">ShortLink</div>

  <h1>404</h1>

  <p class="sub">
    This short link doesn't exist or has already expired.
    It may have been deleted or the URL might be incorrect.
  </p>

  <div class="cards">
    <div class="card">
      <span class="label">Expired</span>
      <p>Links are automatically deleted after their expiry date.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <span class="label">Mistyped</span>
      <p>Double-check the short code — it's case-sensitive.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <span class="label">Deleted</span>
      <p>The owner may have removed this link from their account.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="actions">
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Dashboard</a>
    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost">Sign In</a>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
